Package model.board

Class KillTrack

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.board.KillTrack
  • public class KillTrack
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents the sole killshot track on the game board from which skulls are removed and to which damage tokens are added as players die. Only the standard rules whereby the game goes into Final Frenzy on the 8th and final skull are considered.

    • Constructor Detail

      • KillTrack

        KillTrack()
        Creates a new killtrack filled with skulls. It also creates an empty array of Colour: every time a player is killed, the colour of the killer is added in the array, at the same position as the removed skull.
